        <briefdescription>
<para>Map PCIe TC/VC. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>bdf</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>the target PCI endpoint </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>map</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>the tc/vc map to apply </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 on success, a negative error code otherwise</para>
</simplesect>
Note: VC must be disabled prior to call this function and enabled afterward in order for the endpoint to take advandage of the map.</para>
<para>Note: Not being able to enable such feature is a non-fatal error and any code using it should behave accordingly (displaying some info, and ignoring it for instance). </para>
